data.description: Enjoy “front-porch sitting” at its finest on the graciously-sized, covered porch of this 3 bed, 2 bath ranch style home situated on a 1+acre lot w/ NO HOA! This home features a spacious living room w/brick surround fireplace, while the kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinet & counter space, a breakfast area & walk-in pantry w/built-ins.  Bonus/flex room is perfect for a 2nd living area, home ofc, playroom, etc. All bedrooms are spacious w/ the primary featuring its own bath. Storage space abounds, w/multiple closets & shelving. Neutral colors throughout create the perfect palette to make this home your own. All appliances remain to incl’d refrigerator & W/D. Large yard out back w/ fenced area. Recent updates, per seller: vinyl trim work, lighting upgrades to include outside security lights on 3 sides & multiple electrical outlets on ext. of home. Come see all the charm a small town has to offer while being convenient to Charlotte & Gaston County!
